BL330Purgebml is a BusinessClass
    owned by bl
    prefix is W1430

    Patterns
        disable StaticTranslations
        implements WorkFile

    Persistent Fields
        WorkFile                is UniqueID
        WorkFileSeq             is Numeric size 12
        BmlCompany              is like BillingCompany
        BmlRecurInvoice         is like RecurringInvoiceParameter 
        BmlLineNbr              is like RecurringInvoiceLine 
        BmlItem                 is like Item
        BmlQuantity             is like Quantity 
        BmlSellUom              is like UnitOfMeasure
        BmlUnitPrice            is like InternationalCost
        BmlSprUom               is like UnitOfMeasure
        BmlZeroAfterUse         is Boolean
        BmlStartDate            is Date    
        BmlStopDate             is Date    
        BmlTerritory            is like Territory 
        BmlSalesman             is like SalesRepresentative 
        BmlSalesman2            is like SalesRepresentative 
        BmlCommRate1            is like ChrgRate 
        BmlCommRate2            is like ChrgRate 
        BmlCommSplit            is like CommissionSplitPercentage 
        BmlStdComm1             is like BillingStandardCommentHeader 
        BmlStdComm2             is like BillingStandardCommentHeader 
        BmlStdComm3             is like BillingStandardCommentHeader 
        BmlLastMiscSeq          is like Sequence3 
        BmlLastCommSeq          is like Sequence3 

    Sets

        InsertionOrderSet
            indexed
            no duplicates
            primary
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                WorkFileSeq

    Actions

        Create is a Create Action

            Field Rules
                WorkFileSeq
                    autosequence

        Delete is a Delete Action

        DeleteAll is a Set Action
            restricted

            Parameters
                WorkFileHeader is UniqueID

            Instance Selection
                where (WorkFile = WorkFileHeader)

            Local Fields
                LWorkFileHeader is a WorkFile

            Parameter Rules
                WorkFileHeader
                    required
                    LWorkFileHeader = WorkFileHeader

            Action Rules
                Instance Rules
                    invoke Delete

                Empty Set Rules
                    invoke Purge LWorkFileHeader

                Set Rules
                    Exit Rules
                        invoke Purge LWorkFileHeader
